    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CARD DRAW</strong> 是一个轻松的Roguelike卡组构建游戏，你可以通过构建卡片方程式来获得积分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/e69d8a1a4de441a402643d96fd9b4f14.poster.avif?t=1736167864\" width=788 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/e69d8a1a4de441a402643d96fd9b4f14.webm?t=1736167864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/e69d8a1a4de441a402643d96fd9b4f14.mp4?t=1736167864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >如何游玩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从你的卡组中抽取卡片来<strong>创建方程式</strong>并为你的<strong>最终得分</strong><strong>赚取积分</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用能力卡牌来发现<strong>策略和协同效果</strong>，以获得更多积分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在商店中使用积分</strong>来<strong>扩展你的卡组</strong>，并加入<strong>新卡和能力</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的得分就是你的货币</strong>：你在商店中消费的积分将从你的总得分中扣除，因此需要仔细考虑何时停止购买卡片并开始累积积分。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/fa0b36c86e81c3f22af12816ed140540.poster.avif?t=1736167864\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/fa0b36c86e81c3f22af12816ed140540.webm?t=1736167864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/fa0b36c86e81c3f22af12816ed140540.mp4?t=1736167864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/1685115e943e7d4b6a63828c28d9d913.poster.avif?t=1736167864\" width=790 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/1685115e943e7d4b6a63828c28d9d913.webm?t=1736167864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/1685115e943e7d4b6a63828c28d9d913.mp4?t=1736167864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完整游戏内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7种不同游戏模式</strong>：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放松模式<br>抽卡并看到你的得分上升</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >策略模式<br>抽卡并摆放卡片来构建完美的方程式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelike模式<br>升级并尽可能多地生存</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挂机模式<br>在做其他事情时观看得分增长</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险模式<br>解任务获得新的抽牌并玩更长时间</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡组构建模式<br>用你的收藏卡牌打造完美卡组</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战模式<br>使用卡片解决挑战和数学难题</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在线排行榜</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1000+</strong>卡牌与能力类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam成就</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战、练习模式、卡片收藏等更多内容！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/301e53ca1df767cf80e44285afdeba32.poster.avif?t=1736167864\" width=800 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/301e53ca1df767cf80e44285afdeba32.webm?t=1736167864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261300/extras/301e53ca1df767cf80e44285afdeba32.mp4?t=1736167864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
